  choice3: '<Let the Hound Intimidate Him> '
  choice3Outcome: "\u201CThe Hound barks at the man intimidatingly, but instead of
    fleeing or fighting he begins to lower his axe.\n\u2018Oh! I didn\u2019t realize
    you were also victims of her schemes, my mistake! You must be on the run then,
    correct? I would\u2019ve done the same if it weren\u2019t for\u2026 nevermind.
    Let me give you some food, I have plenty, and it\u2019s not like I need to go
    anywhere\u2019\nAn unexpected outcome, but a welcome one. You leave wondering
    what exactly the Red Queen did to make a man act like that.\u201D\n[The Hound
    gains +10 Max Hp, all Party Members gain 5 HP.]\n"
